song_lyrics: Chhapaiyāmā janmyātā, jay jay Shrī Ghanshyāmjī,
Mitro sāthe ramyātā, jay jay Shrī Ghanshyāmjī,
Māt-pitāne gamyātā.... Jay jay Shrī Ghanshyāmjī,
Devo sarve namyātā... Jay jay Shrī Ghanshyāmjī,
Bolo Ghanshyām Mahārājnī jay... 1
Vannī vāṭ līdhītī... Jay jay Shrī Nīlkanṭhjī,
Tapashcharyā kīdhītī... Jay jay Shrī Nīlkanṭhjī,
Sāchī rāh chīndhītī... Jay jay Shrī Nīlkanṭhjī,
Mukti saune dīdhītī... Jay jay Shrī Nīlkanṭhjī,
Nolo Nīlkanṭh Varṇī Mahārājnī jay... 2
Paramhanso karyātā... Jay jay Sahajānandjī,
Moṭā mandir bāndhyātā... Jay jay Sahajānandjī,
Samaiyāo bharyātā... Jay jay Sahajānandjī,
Jannā dukho haryātā... Jay jay Sahajānandjī,
Bolo Sahajānand Swāmī Mahārājnī jay... 3
Shikṣhāpatrī āpītī... Jay jay Swāminārāyaṇ,
Samādhī karāvītī, jay jay Swāminārāyaṇ,
Mokṣhnī vāt māpītī... Jay jay Swāminārāyaṇ,
Akṣharvāṭ sthāpītī... Jay jay Swāminārāyaṇ,
Bolo Swāminārāyaṇ Bhagwānnī jay... 4
title: Chhapaiyāmā janmyātā jay jay Shrī Ghanshyāmjī
